100
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,440
Dudes, come out quickly.

101
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:20,136
We need to film the line sync now,
or we won’t get it edited in time.

102
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,880
Fine. I’m here.

103
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:25,040
I’m here. I’m here. I’m here. I’m here.

104
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,120
Are you done?

105
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,680
Where’s Thame?

106
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,576
I think he’s meeting us
at the filming location.

107
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,616
