126
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,480
Jun.

127
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:35,240
Showing some respect is good, Thame.

128
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,720
But you should have figured
out if he wanted some respect

129
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:38,920
or something else.

130
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,520
I asked him to watch a movie with me,

131
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,016
