actually watch it, right?

132
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:44,240
Didn’t you know this sentence is slang?

133
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:46,416
It doesn’t always mean
"Let’s watch a movie" literally.

134
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:49,000
It can also mean "Let’s have sex."

135
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,560
Yeah.

136
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,600
Do you think

137
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,880
